[{"question":"How is your family coping with this?","answer":"Very privately.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":37,"aSentId":38},{"question":"What kind of girl was Olivia?","answer":"She was a warm -- she was outgoing.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":44,"aSentId":45},{"question":"What does this say about America that this is happening, do you think?","answer":"I think that this isn\u0027t only about America, I think this is part of the human condition.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":61,"aSentId":62},{"question":"Is it any comfort at all to the family, to Olivia\u0027s parents, Brian and Shannon, that the whole world is grieving with them and for them?","answer":"Yes, the Facebook page we put up -- they didn\u0027t ask for that.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":74,"aSentId":75},{"question":"What is your view about this debate?","answer":"I have to tell you, I don\u0027t consider myself an expert and I didn\u0027t think that that\u0027s the kind of thing that you want me on the show for.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":90,"aSentId":91},{"question":"ORGAN: You didn\u0027t have any place in civilian hands in America?","answer":"I have to say -- I\u0027d have to say no.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":95,"aSentId":96},{"question":"Can you try and explain to me why you believe the answer to this is to arm teachers?","answer":"Well, the alternative is what we have seen, where people were reduced to waiting to be murdered, without able -- being able to do anything effective to protect themselves or the adults, to protect the children.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":111,"aSentId":112},{"question":"Why where the teachers put the guns?","answer":"People can carry firearms in a concealed fashion.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":122,"aSentId":123},{"question":"It is this, why do you believe, given that you have 300 million guns in circulation and the worst gun crime rate in any of the civilized countries of the world, that more guns is the answer to less gun murder?","answer":"Because the problem occurs, sir, in those areas precisely where we have said no guns.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":156,"aSentId":157},{"question":"From guns?","answer":"It\u0027s under three for 100,000 and in Fairfax County where Gun Owners of America is located --","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":165,"aSentId":166},{"question":"What is your view?","answer":"I think we need to ban gun control laws that keep people from being able to protect themselves.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":175,"aSentId":176},{"question":"You\u0027re an unbelievably stupid man, aren\u0027t you?","answer":"It seems to me that you\u0027re morally obtuse.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":200,"aSentId":201},{"question":"It seems to me that facts don\u0027t bother you, do they, Mr. Morgan?","answer":"-- is the right for any -- Americans -- you would like to see --","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":211,"aSentId":212},{"question":"How many -- how many guns did Mrs. Lanza have in her home?","answer":"I don\u0027t know how many she had.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":219,"aSentId":220},{"question":"And you would be quite happy if there are many more people in his position, in homes around America, where there are that number of firearms, which could be used by mentally unstable people?","answer":"Americans with firearms in their homes typically have them locked in a safe.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":236,"aSentId":237},{"question":"How can you say such a thing?","answer":"Let me finish my sentence.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":252,"aSentId":253},{"question":"Is that the solution to America\u0027s gun murder problems?","answer":"I would challenge you to go and tell the Korean merchants who survived the riots in Los Angeles, sorry, you had those firearms that saved your lives.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":263,"aSentId":264},{"question":"Can you answer my question?","answer":"I\u0027m answering your question.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":265,"aSentId":266},{"question":"Well, the press tend to do that, don\u0027t they?","answer":"Stop being so facetious.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":277,"aSentId":278},{"question":"Post what happened at Sandy Hook, your answer to this problem of repeated use of this weapon with these high-capacity magazines is to continue letting Americans buy them with impunity, and to not concern yourself with these mass shootings, is that right?","answer":"The Second Amendment means what it says, and meanwhile, you want to continue laws against self-defense.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":280,"aSentId":281},{"question":"Carolyn McCarthy, when you hear this and you hear the way that debate is framed, what is your reaction?","answer":"Well, to be very honest with you, I\u0027m very happy that you had him on, because I think America should see what we\u0027re up against and the lies that they take to the American people, and unfortunately, an awful lot of them believe that.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":314,"aSentId":315},{"question":"Or are other Americans going to rise up and say enough?","answer":"Well, I believe this terrible tragedy, taking the lives of 20 little people, the same age as my two youngest granddaughters, has affected America in such a deep way, that we\u0027re in a position to have, not just a discussion, but the action that I think is necessary to prevent a reoccurrence.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":331,"aSentId":332},{"question":"Or is it just going to be another statistic in the mass shooting catalog, which is getting worse and worse?","answer":"I think you\u0027re right.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":380,"aSentId":381},{"question":"How do you change the mentality that says really any American, as Mr. Pratt, believes -- the answer to any of these shootings is to arm everybody else with the same kind of weapons?","answer":"See, I don\u0027t think it\u0027s the American culture.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":414,"aSentId":415},{"question":"Where are those politicians?","answer":"They are around.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":449,"aSentId":450},{"question":"Could that happen?","answer":"Absolutely.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":489,"aSentId":490},{"question":"What was your experience like?","answer":"Well, two main things in my mind dominated the conversation.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":523,"aSentId":524},{"question":"From that what we know about his profile, what do you think has happened here?","answer":"Well, the common thread, going beyond what you talked about, is that there is a motive.","docId":"121218pmt","qSentId":537,"aSentId":538}]